# GitHub Actions / Render 에 넣을 환경변수 목록 (값은 대시보드에서 직접 입력)

# ── GitHub → Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions ──
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://YOUR-RENDER-APP.onrender.com/api/v1
# RENDER_DEPLOY_HOOK_URL=https://api.render.com/deploy/srv-XXXX?key=YYYY
#
# Deploy Hook: Render -> machinefit-api -> Settings -> Deploy Hook -> Create/copy URL
# If Render Auto-Deploy (GitHub) is already on, disable one to avoid double deploys.

# ── Render (무료) → New → Web Service — Blueprint 아님 ──
# Root Directory: (비움, monorepo 루트)
# Build: npm ci --include=dev && npm run build:render
# Start: npm run start --workspace=backend
# Instance: Free | Health: /api/v1/health
#
# ── Render → machinefit-api → Environment ──
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres.PROJECT_REF:PASSWORD@aws-1-ap-northeast-2.pooler.supabase.com:5432/postgres
# JWT_SECRET=(32자 이상 랜덤 문자열)
# JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=(다른 32자 이상 랜덤 문자열)
# CORS_ORIGIN=https://madbandi-star.github.io

# ── 로컬 개발 (backend/.env) ──
# config/env/.env.example 참고
